    <tr>
      <td style="font-size:11px !important;">If you do not agree with our decision about whether or not you are an eligible employer, you have a right to appeal our decision and receive a hearing. Employers have the right to appeal a denial of eligibility, the failure of Health Connector to provide a timely eligibility determination, or the failure of the Health Connector to provide a timely notice of an eligibility determination.</td>
